---
title: Mexican Plant-Based Mince & Bean Chilli with Jacket Potatoes & Tomato Salsa
description: Our plant-based mince is taken to a new level with our Mexican Fiesta spice blend. While it comes with a spicy warning, you can tailor it your tastebuds by adding as little (or as much!) as you’d like. Cool things down with a fresh salad and some plant-based mayo.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
